Package com.flipkart.DAO

Class FlipFitAdminDAOImplementation

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.DAO.FlipFitAdminDAOImplementation
All Implemented Interfaces:
FlipFitAdminDAOInterface
public class FlipFitAdminDAOImplementation extends Object implements FlipFitAdminDAOInterface
This class implements the FlipFitAdminDAOInterface and provides the functionality for managing the admin actions in the FlipFit Gym system, including viewing gyms, customers, gym owners, updating the admin profile, and verifying gyms and gym owners.
